    <briefdescription>
<para>The wheel event class is used to store a wheel rolling, it facilitates processing of the wheel rolling and passing to other libraries like Toolkit. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>There is a key modifier which relates to keys like alt, shift and control functions are supplied to check if they have been pressed when the wheel is being rolled.</para>
<para>We support a mouse device and there may be another custom device that support the wheel event. The device type is specified as <emphasis>type</emphasis>. The mouse wheel event can be sent to the specific actor but the custom wheel event will be sent to the stage. @SINCE_1_0.0 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
